<p>Next improvements planned for the new UHF-&gt;UHF stability code:<br>
A) For stability_analysis follow, move the SCF control from stability to SCF code. This means SCF should control the whole SCF procedure. Stability reoptimizations would be a macroloop nesting the SCF:<br>
`&lt;do {<br>
    do {<br>
            Get D, F, etc...<br>
            Compute energy<br>
            compute convergence criterion<br>
           } while (not converged and (SCF_iterations &lt; MAX_SCF_iterations ) )<br>
      if stability_analysis {<br>
         stability()<br>
      }<br>
      } while (not stable and (num_attempts &lt; MAX_num_attempts) )</p>

<p>HF::finalize()&gt;`</p>

<p>B) Improve the old PK code by either finding a way to use PK integrals for Davidson algorithm, or at least saving the transformed MOs used to build the Hessian. Right now, CCSD computations with PK and stability analysis do the AO-&gt;MO transformation twice.</p>

<p>Any problem/suggestions on that ?</p>

